trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> provides data about a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> event.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> fornisce i dati su un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> evento.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> object provides the following information:
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs> oggetto fornisce le informazioni seguenti:

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> property that references the component being renamed.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> proprietà che fa riferimento il componente da rinominare.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> property that indicates the old name of the component.
trans-unit.target: Un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> proprietà che indica il nome precedente del componente.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> property that indicates the new name of the component.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> proprietà che indica il nuovo nome del componente.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates creating a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come creare un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs>.
